# QA Report — Foundation: Routes, Models, Translations
**Date:** 2026-02-28
**Branch:** feat/onboarding-first-half
**Plan task:** #1 — Setup foundation

---

## Test Results Overview

| Suite | Total | Pass | Fail | Skip |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| widget_test.dart | 5 | 5 | 0 | 0 |
